Privacy Policy
Effective Date: 2024-3-1

We, at AlrashedSmart/Flash Anzan, prioritize your privacy and are committed to protecting it through our compliance with this policy. This policy describes our practices regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of your information through the Alrashed Smart Flash Anzan application, and outlines your privacy rights.

Collection of Information
We do not collect personal information directly from our users. However, we may collect non-personally identifiable information that your device provides to us in connection with your use of our app, such as device type and OS version.

Use of Information
The information we collect is used solely for enhancing the app functionality and improving user experience. It is not shared with any third parties.

Data Security
We employ industry-standard security measures to protect the information collected. However, no security system is impenetrable. We cannot guarantee the security of our databases, nor can we guarantee that the information you supply will not be intercepted while being transmitted to us over the Internet.

User Rights
You have the right to request access to the personal data we hold about you, to request corrections, or to request deletion of your data. Please contact us at the details below to make such requests.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "2024-3-1" at the top. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us via email at qotadadmour@gmail.com.
